sequenceDiagram
    participant Store as Pinia Store
    participant API as Elysia API
    participant Cache as InMemoryCache
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note over Store,DB: Pertama kali app dibuka — cache kosong
    Store->>API: GET /api/v1/folders
    API->>Cache: get("all-folders")
    Cache-->>API: null (miss)
    API->>DB: SELECT * FROM folders
    DB-->>API: rows
    API->>Cache: set("all-folders", data, ttl=30s)
    API-->>Store: FolderDto[]

    Note over Store,DB: Request kedua dalam 30 detik
    Store->>API: GET /api/v1/folders
    API->>Cache: get("all-folders")
    Cache-->>API: FolderDto[] (hit — skip DB)
    API-->>Store: FolderDto[]

    Note over Store,DB: User buat / rename / pindah / hapus folder
    Store->>API: POST /api/v1/folders (atau PATCH / DELETE)
    API->>Cache: invalidate("all-folders")
    API->>DB: INSERT / UPDATE / DELETE
    DB-->>API: hasil mutasi
    API-->>Store: FolderDto (data terbaru)
    Store->>Store: update state lokal langsung

    Note over Store,DB: Request berikutnya — cache sudah kosong lagi
    Store->>API: GET /api/v1/folders
    API->>Cache: get("all-folders")
    Cache-->>API: null (miss — refetch fresh)
    API->>DB: SELECT * FROM folders
    DB-->>API: rows (termasuk perubahan terbaru)
    API->>Cache: set("all-folders", data, ttl=30s)
    API-->>Store: FolderDto[]
